#: src/helper/kcmgrub2.actions:2
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "GRUB2 Bootloader Control Module"
msgstr "GRUB2 부트로더 제어 모듈"

#: src/helper/kcmgrub2.actions:50
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Restore the default GRUB2 Bootloader settings"
msgstr "기본 GRUB2 부트로더 설정 복원"

#: src/helper/kcmgrub2.actions:94
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"Administrator authorization is required to restore the default GRUB2 "
"Bootloader settings"
msgstr "기본 GRUB2 부트로더 설정을 복원하려면 관리자 인증이 필요합니다"

#: src/helper/kcmgrub2.actions:141
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Install the GRUB2 Bootloader"
msgstr "GRUB2 부트로더 설치"

#: src/helper/kcmgrub2.actions:187
msgctxt "Description"
msgid "Administrator authorization is required to install the GRUB2 Bootloader"
msgstr "GRUB2 부트로더를 설치하려면 관리자 인증이 필요합니다"

#: src/helper/kcmgrub2.actions:235
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Load the GRUB2 Bootloader settings"
msgstr "GRUB2 부트로더 설정 가져오기"

#: src/helper/kcmgrub2.actions:281
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"Administrator authorization is required to load the GRUB2 Bootloader settings"
msgstr "GRUB2 부트로더 설정을 가져오려면 관리자 인증이 필요합니다"

#: src/helper/kcmgrub2.actions:329
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Save the GRUB2 Bootloader settings"
msgstr "GRUB2 부트로더 설정 저장"

#: src/helper/kcmgrub2.actions:374
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"Administrator authorization is required to save the GRUB2 Bootloader settings"
msgstr "GRUB2 부트로더 설정을 저장하려면 관리자 인증이 필요합니다"

